In this installment of ASME’s “Engineering Influencers” series, our subject is Kaemen Lafleur, aka “Kaemen the Creator” - an innovative engineer whose imagination runs wild with the projects he builds. 👨‍🔬

From exoskeletons to flamethrowers, Kaemen is pushing the boundaries of what’s possible with mechanical engineering. 🛠️

And while there is a definite “fun-factor” to the mechanical concepts Kaemen devises, what’s even more exciting is thinking of the real world impact these inventions might have one day. 🌍
